These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-3-1::.
7 different games are played: bridge, chess, monopoly, go, backgammon, canasta, poker
There are 7 different favourite colors: ivory, fuchsia, red, coral, blood-red, green, aquamarine
 1. the person playing backgammon is on the left of the person who likes green##1
 2. the person who likes ivory is the person playing poker##1
 3. the person playing canasta is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person who likes blood-red is on the left or right of the person who likes ivory##3
 5. the person playing bridge is on the right of the person who likes coral##1
 6. the person playing monopoly is on the left of the person who likes coral##1
 7. the person who likes blood-red is on the left of the person who likes ivory##1
 8. the person who likes aquamarine is on the left or right of the person who likes fuchsia##3
 9. the person playing canasta is on the left of the person playing go##1
10. the person playing go is the person who likes fuchsia##1
11. the person playing go is between the person who likes red and the person playing monopoly##2
12. the person who likes blood-red is on the right of the person who likes green##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3   |    4    |   5   |    6     |    7    |
| Game   | canasta  | go | monopoly  | backgammon | bridge | chess | poker |
| Color           | red | fuchsia   | aquamarine | coral  | green   | blood-red    | ivory    |

