.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-3-2::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: musical, martial-arts, superhero, comedy, time-travel, sports, scientific
7 different pets are kept: rat, pony, goldfish, fish, ferret, goat, lizard
 1. the owner of the goldfish is on the left or right of the person watching scientific movies##3
 2. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1
 3. the person watching time-travel movies is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person watching superhero movies is on the far left or far right##3
 5. the owner of the goat is in the middle##1
 6. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the person watching musical movies##1
 7. the owner of the goldfish is on the left or right of the owner of the fish##3
 8. the person watching comedy movies is between the owner of the ferret and the owner of the pony##2
 9. the owner of the fish is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
10. the person watching superhero movies is on the left or right of the person watching comedy movies##3
11. the owner of the rat is on the right of the owner of the pony##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |   3    |      4      |    5     |    6    |    7     |
| Movie-Genre      | superhero | comedy | sports   | martial-arts | scientific | musical     | time-travel |
| Pet   | pony     | rat  | ferret | goat     | lizard  | goldfish | fish |

