 3. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1
 4. the person driving the subway is in the middle##1
 5. the person driving the motorbike is the person who's birthday is in august##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in february is the person driving the car##1
 7. the person driving the boat is on the left or right of the person driving the trike##3
 8. the person driving the jet-ski is the person who's birthday is in june##1
 9. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person driving the car##1
10. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in september##3
11. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person driving the boat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2    |     3      |      4      |      5      |       6       |     7      |
