 4. the person who growsbellflower is the fonseca-smoker##1
 5. the montecristo-smoker is on the left or right of the old-henry-smoker##3
 6. the person who growsdaisy is on the left of the person who growsdahlia##1
 7. the old-henry-smoker is between the person who growsdahlia and the person who growsazalea##2
 8. the person who growsbellflower is on the left or right of the person who growssunflower##3
 9. the dannemann-smoker is on the right of the fonseca-smoker##1
10. the person who growsbellflower is on the left or right of the prince-smoker##3
11. the person who growsiris is on the right of the person who growsrose##1

.:: Answer ::.
