 3. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the person eating lime##1
 4. the person eating lime is the ranch-style house##1
 5. the person eating cabbage is on the right of the cape-cod house##1
 6. the person eating nectarine is on the left or right of the craftsman house##3
 7. the craftsman house is on the far left##1
 8. the cape-cod house is between the modern house and the person eating lime##2
 9. the person eating lime is on the right of the person eating kale##1
10. the art-deco house is on the left or right of the person eating onion##3
11. the modern house is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |   2    |   3    |      4       |     5      |    6     |   7    |
| Food   | onion         | nectarine | garlic   | kale        | lime  | avocado  | cabbage |
| House         | craftsman | art-deco  | colonial | gothic-revival | ranch-style | cape-cod | modern |

