.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-3-20::.
7 different games are played: backgammon, go, poker, canasta, scrabble, chess, domino
There are 7 different nationalities: french, canadian, spanish, australian, egyptian, malaysian, colombian
 1. the colombian is the person playing canasta##1
 2. the person playing backgammon is on the left or right of the colombian##3
 3. the person playing backgammon is on the left or right of the person playing scrabble##3
 4. the egyptian is on the left or right of the person playing domino##3
 5. the australian is on the left of the canadian##1
 6. the person playing canasta is on the far left##1
 7. the canadian is between the egyptian and the person playing scrabble##2
 8. the malaysian is on the right of the person playing go##1
 9. the spanish is the person playing chess##1
10. the french is on the left or right of the australian##3
11. the canadian is the person playing poker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |   2    |       3       |     4     |    5    |      6       |      7      |
| Game           | canasta | backgammon   | scrabble | poker    | go   | domino | chess     |
| Nationality   | colombian    | french | australian        | canadian | egyptian | malaysian   | spanish |

 